works for me on archlinux with ABS (https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/ABS)

install:
download xep136_plugin.h, xep136_plugin.c and Makefile and run these commands
	$ make
	$ make install
	$ make clean

another method:
download pidgin source code, xep136_plugin.c, xep136_plugin.h and run these commands
	$ tar xjvf pidgin-2.10.0.tar.bz2 
	$ mv xep136_plugin.c xep136_plugin.h pidgin-2.10.0/pidgin/plugins/
	$ cd pidgin-2.10.0/
	$ ./configure
	$ cd pidgin/plugins/
	$ make xep136_plugin.so
	$ mkdir ~/.purple/plugins/
	$ cp xep136_plugin.so ~/.purple/plugins/
